{"id":570480,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/10/【立此存照】新华社在英国报纸以广告形式刊登捧/","date":"2017-10-20T00:35:22Z","modified":"2017-10-20T00:35:22Z","title":"【立此存照】新华社在英国报纸以广告形式刊登捧习文章","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>当地时间2017年10月17日，新华社在英国《每日电讯报》以文章的形式发布了整版彩色广告，推广所谓“习式外交” (Xiplomacy)。这种广告形式，若不注意报纸右上角的声明，乍看之下就好像是《每日电讯》刊登了整版吹捧习近平的文章。</p>\n<p>经查询，《每日电讯报》整版彩色广告目前最新的官方报价在5.9万英镑 (折合人民币约51万元) 与6.8万英镑之间(折合人民币约59万元)。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-lang=\"en\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">Astonishing. Today&#8217;s Telegraph has full-page advertorial hailing wisdom &amp; humanity of Xi Jinping written by Chinese state news agency Xinhua <a href=\"https://t.co/rjYCUMILVM\">pic.twitter.com/rjYCUMILVM</a></p>\n<p>— Peter Walker (@peterwalker99) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/peterwalker99/status/920222954050514944?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 17, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读</strong>：<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/09/%E3%80%90%E7%9C%9F%EF%BD%A5%E5%9C%9F%E8%B1%AA%E3%80%91%E3%80%8A%E7%BA%BD%E6%97%B6%E3%80%8B%E8%BF%8E%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E8%8A%B1%E8%B4%B9%E6%88%96%E5%B0%86%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">【真･土豪】《纽时》迎习近平访美广告花费或达百万美元(组图)</a></p></blockquote>\n<p>中共很显然对这次十九大的外宣下了很大一番功夫，在报刊外还投放了大量网络广告。有海外网友表示自己在十九大开幕当天收到了不少推广大会直播的网络广告：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_570481\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/0066lZpZly1fklbqybm8aj31d20ba7qs.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-570481\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/0066lZpZly1fklbqybm8aj31d20ba7qs.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"138\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/0066lZpZly1fklbqybm8aj31d20ba7qs.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/0066lZpZly1fklbqybm8aj31d20ba7qs-300x69.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/0066lZpZly1fklbqybm8aj31d20ba7qs-768x176.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">网友贴出的网络广告截图；微博图片</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[30303,30129,20377]}